Here are some tips for writing effective emails:
- in the same way I'm writing the content of this email, please use bullet points to summarize clearly;
- the subject line should be coincise and not too long;
- only copy the people that are needed, understanding the differences between cc and ccn;
- be sure that the attachments are correct;
- use a polite tone. Expressions such as "Please fell free to contact me" are appreciated;
- it is a good practice to not use emoticons to avoid misunderstandings.

I hope that these suggestions can be helpful to you.
Best regards

